<i>Will seeing a psychiatrist help Jessica?</i>

23:27.472 --> 23:29.473
<i>Will seeing Jessica</i>
<i>help the psychiatrist?</i>

23:29.474 --> 23:30.975
<i>Now that Eunice has left home,</i>

23:30.976 --> 23:32.476
<i>will Corinne end up</i>
<i>with her room?</i>

23:32.477 --> 23:34.478
<i>Her clothes? Her man?</i>

23:34.479 --> 23:36.480
<i>Did Carol just drop by</i>
<i>to see the baby</i>

23:36.481 --> 23:38.482
<i>or does she really want</i>
<i>something else?</i>

23:38.483 --> 23:40.484
<i>Now that Burt knows</i>
<i>he's not going to die,</i>

23:40.485 --> 23:42.987
<i>will finding out</i>
<i>Mary's baby might not be his</i>

23:42.988 --> 23:43.988
<i>kill him?</i>

23:43.989 --> 23:45.489
<i>These questions and many others</i>

23:45.490 --> 23:48.493
<i>will be answered</i>
<i>on the next episode of...</i> Soap.

